::Prowl/Striker::

Prowl frowns as he sees Iron Raptor walk off stumbling toward the Ark. He looks at the trail of mechfluid she was leaving.

"I really think you should get to a CR chamber first," he says, catching up to Iron Raptor, "The meeting can wait."

Striker lands behind the two. "I seem to remember ordering you to a CR chamber, Prowl," he says rather disapointingly, "Tell you what. You both go to CR chambers, and I will inform Liono that you will be slightly late for the meeting."
